      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "This seems like a significant behavior change. The way I read this, `InvalidateCoinsDBOnDisk` is only called by `MaybeCompleteSnapshotValidation`. Its return type is ignored by its call site in `ConnectTip`, which I think would now lead us to skip over some code afterwards. ",
